LanguageData.Hakuro_Royal_Kaiser.label: Fenris Kaiser
LanguageData.Hakuro_Royal_Kaiser.description: Leader of the Unknown Snow World
LanguageData.Hakuro_Stranger.label: snowfield Stranger
LanguageData.Hakuro_Stranger.description: Visitors who come to the snowfield for the first time think it is unfamiliar.
LanguageData.Hakuro_Visitors.label: snowfield visitant
LanguageData.Hakuro_Visitors.description: This title symbolizes visitors who have continued to interact with and helped with Seolwon.
LanguageData.Hakuro_citizen.label: snowfield citizen
LanguageData.Hakuro_citizen.description: It is a title recognized as a citizen who can live in the world of snow.
LanguageData.Hakuro_Hunter.label: snowfield Hunter
LanguageData.Hakuro_Hunter.description: A title promoted to Snowfield Hunter. You have some support rights, so you can ask for help when you need it.
LanguageData.Hakuro_Grimbart.label: snowfield Grimbart
LanguageData.Hakuro_Grimbart.description: Snowfield Grimbart Hunter's mandate gives you higher benefits.
LanguageData.Hakuro_Isegrim.label: snowfield Isegrim
LanguageData.Hakuro_Isegrim.description: Snowfield Nowgrim is a kind of sub-title, but with influence, unlocking most of its powers.
LanguageData.Hakuro_Sirius.label: snowfield Sirius
LanguageData.Hakuro_Sirius.description: Snowfield Sirius is freed from various powers, and also has the right to trade with the Shadow Fleet that helped him pass on the spirit magic of the white wolf.
LanguageData.Hakuro_Fenris.label: snowfield Fenris
LanguageData.Hakuro_Fenris.description: It doesn't seem like much to accept those from outside the snowfields into Fenris. However, accepting people from the outside can be seen as having a high level of influence.
